==Polish==

===Noun===
'''Politechnika'''
# Institution of higher education (typically accepting students from the age of about 19, depending on country, but in some cases able to take younger students in exceptional cases) where technical subjects are studied and researched in depth and degrees are offered.

===Translations===
*Polish: [[politechnika]] ''f''
*English: [[University of Technology]], [[Technological University]], [[Polytechnic Institute]] ''m''

